<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />We do not see any more signs;</para>

<para style="q1">there is no prophet any more,</para>

<para style="q1">and no one among us knows how long this will last.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="10" style="v" />How long, God, will the enemy throw insults at you?</para>

<para style="q1">Will the enemy blaspheme your name forever?</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="11" style="v" />Why do you hold back your hand, your right hand?</para>

<para style="q1">Take your right hand from your garment and destroy them.</para>

